story: Narendra Modi added 11 new photos to the album: Vibrant Gujarat 2017.
caption: Vibrant Gujarat 2017 has brought together several world leaders, ministers from overseas nations, business leaders and young entrepreneurs. Here are some glimpses of my meetings in Gandhinagar during Vibrant Gujarat 2017.
